text: Madeline Carroll (born ) is an American actress known for starring as Juli Baker in Flipped, as Molly Johnson in Swing Vote, as Farren in The Spy Next Door, and as Willow O'Neil The Magic of Belle Isle. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1996 births Category:American Christians Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American child actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:Living people
